This article is a transcript of remarks made by President Trump at a gathering of student leaders from colleges and universities in the United States. The President praises the achievements of the young Americans and highlights the success of his administration, including recent Supreme Court decisions and the booming economy. He emphasizes the importance of free speech and the right to bear arms, as well as the need for a strong military and secure borders. The President also discusses job opportunities, tax cuts, trade deals, and the importance of following one's passion and never giving up. He concludes by expressing his gratitude and wishing the students success in their future endeavors.